<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>حَيْثُ لَا بَيِّنَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>حَتَّى يقدم الْغَائِب فَإِن كَانَ للْمُدَّعى بَيِّنَة قضى<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
